node.text:
Its summertime and soon enough school will be starting! And best of all fall sports is back! As a former high school media teacher I loved filming sports especially the football games, Friday nite lights! There is nothing like it!

The best part is now coaches, parents and students can now capture all these moments with their mobile device like the iPhone or iPad. 

So August 7th at 10 am Pacific I will be live streaming a free training session called Filming Sports with your mobile device. If you are a parent filming recruiting videos for you child, a coach filming games or practice, or a teacher/student who is tasked with filming sports, this training is perfect for you.

Inside this special training I will dive into all my secrets from my award winning high school media class that filmed all the sports events, plays, and community events. 

We will dive into some basics of mobile devices, which apps are best in class, how to edit and even live stream on the go!

Whether you a just starting out using mobile devices or a seasoned pro there will be something for everyone. 

So click on the link below to register for the free training session, and it will connect you to our messenger to alert you connected with us. 

Oh and there will also be a free giveaway so don’t miss out!

Ill see you Saturday August 7th at 10am pacific

Link in profile! 

#fallsports #edtech #highschoolfootball #training #mobilevideo #highschoolsports #edtechteachers
